<dd>Fainites, you are to be complimented on achieving an FA that does have wide readership: <a href="" title="Attachment theory">Attachment theory</a><a class="externallink" href="http://stats.grok.se/en/201001/Attachment_theory" rel="nofollow" title="http://stats.grok.se/en/201001/Attachment_theory"><a class="externallink" href="http://stats.grok.se/en/201001/Attachment_theory" rel="nofollow" title="http://stats.grok.se/en/201001/Attachment_theory">http://stats.grok.se/en/201001/Attachment_theory</a></a>.  —<a href="" title="User:Mattisse">&#60;font color=&#34;navy&#34;&#62;<b>mattisse</b>&#60;/font&#62;</a> (<a href="" title="User talk:Mattisse">Talk</a>) 16:23, 31 January 2010 (UTC)
