<dd>I agree that established editors are often downright hostile to newcomers and have experienced this numerous times while editing without logging it. Every time it happens I feel so sad for the new user who doesn&#39;t yet know how to stand up for himself. <a href="" title="User:Calliopejen1">Calliopejen1</a> (<a href="" title="User talk:Calliopejen1">talk</a>) 21:36, 24 July 2009 (UTC)
